medications.name: Sertraline
medications.response: Inadequate response (poor symptom control) at prior 50mg dose after 4 weeks.
medications.adherence: Excellent (patient reported taking 50mg daily as prescribed)

changes_made.rationale: Inadequate clinical response to 50mg daily after 4 weeks of treatment, given severe depressive symptoms (early morning awakening, severe guilt, functional impairment). Increase to 100mg daily to reach therapeutic effect.
